      "value": "<p>Your bond with your companion deepens, allowing it to anticipate your commands.</p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisites: </strong>Creature Companion Expert, Survival 10 ranks.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Benefit: </strong>Each round on your turn, after you act and only if you didn&rsquo;t grant your creature companion any actions, your creature companion can either take a move action or standard action in addition to its normal move action, or forgo its normal move action and make a full attack. It takes a &ndash;6 penalty to full attacks made using this ability. You can control your creature companion at a range of 80 feet.</p>",
